1. cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with the mathematical theory of epistemic updates and axiomatizes the intuitionistic analogue of the logic of epistemic knowledge and actions.
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper deals with reasoning of agents in an epistemic scenario.
3. cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is likely as the paper uses duality theory to develop the mathematical theory of epistemic updates.
4. cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is possible as the paper deals with the complexity of epistemic updates.
5. cs.PL (Programming Languages) is possible as the paper deals with the construction of complex algebras associated with the given model.
